  "url": "https://www.ada.lk/breaking_news/\u0d85\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dca-\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dcf-\u0d9c\u0ddd\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dc6\u0dda\u0dca\u0dc3\u0dca-\u0db4\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dd2\u0dba\u0da7-\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dc0-\u0d87\u0dad\u0dd2-\u0dc4\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dba-\u0d94\u0dc0\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca-\u0d85\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dbb-\u0d9c\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf/11-396421",
  "time_ut": 1660833850,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dcf \u0d9c\u0ddd\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dc6\u0dda\u0dca\u0dc3\u0dca \u0db4\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dd2\u0dba\u0da7 \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dc0 \u0d87\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0dc4\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dba \u0d94\u0dc0\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d85\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dbb \u0d9c\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The damage caused to the golf course due to the protesters will be recovered from them",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Prasanna Ranatunga, Minister of Urban Development and Housing, said that necessary legal measures will be taken to recover the damage caused to the golf face land due to the long stay of the activists.",
        "The minister said that this group, who are known as militants, have entered the area without permission and have done a lot of wrongdoing to the people. He also mentioned that they have received information that they have established an illegal residence there and have even taken measures to get the addresses to confirm the residence.",
        "\u201cThe golf course where the militants were staying is public property. This is in accordance with section 3(1) of the Urban Development Authority Act No. 41 of 1971 under the Municipal Council Jurisdiction of Colombo where this unauthorized construction is located by the Special Municipal Gazette of the Democratic Socialist Republic of Sri Lanka No. 4/1 dated 30/09/1978. It has been declared a development area.",
        "Therefore, if a temporary construction is carried out in such an urban development area, a permit should be obtained in accordance with Section 8(A)1 of the Urban Development Authority (Amendment) Act No. 04 of 1982.",
        "The Supreme Court has decided that this area should be developed and reserved for public services by the decision of the Supreme Court Case No. 44/2004 THE ENVIRONMENTAL FOUNDATION LIMITED v. Urban Development Authority.",
        "This group, who are known as militants, have entered the area without permission and committed many atrocities.",
        "We have received information that they have entered a public property and established an illegal residence in it and even arranged to get addresses to confirm that residence.",
        "Due to the fact that many unauthorized constructions have been built in the area, the right of the general public to freely use the area has been hindered. It is also affected by the Supreme Court judgment.",
        "All these actions are in violation of the Urban Development Act. Accordingly, the Authority has been empowered to deal with the Urban Development Act No. 41 of 1978 in accordance with Section 28 (a) 3 of Act No. 44 of 82 and Act No. 44 of 84."
      ],
